      "id": "PopularPost21675",
      "post_content": "Actually, in the earlier days white's abilities were more about healing and damage prevention. Red was, and I think still is, the color of war and damage infliction. The *defense* factor of his ability is more of a detente effect. He can be a thorn in your side if you aren't controlling him. He's fun in EDH.",
      "posted_by": "Plantboy81",
